<item>
            <title>[LU-7835] Improved gerrit/checkpatch.pl integration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7835</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The gerrit/checkpatch integration currently runs as a daemon process polling every five minutes but could instead be run as a gerrit job itself allowing it to be triggered.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The coding standards URL has also changed and it would be possible to set command line options allowing invocation of upstream checkpatch.pl if desired.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
